Go bindings for GLUT : https://github.com/rhencke/Go-GLUT

Requires: https://github.com/banthar/Go-OpenGL (for basic OpenGL data types)

If you are using Mac OS X, and are unable to install Go-OpenGL, please apply Go-OpenGL.patch:
    patch -p1 -d your/path/to/Go-OpenGL < Go-OpenGL.patch
    cd your/path/to/Go-OpenGL
    make

To install Go-GLUT:
    make install

To compile examples:
    cd examples
    make

Before calling any other function, call glut.Init()

Tested on Mac OS X... if you have problems on another platform, please let me know (sorry)